										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(g)<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="0" italic="1" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Prototype for secondary bathrooms.</CHARFORMAT> The prototype of a bathroom with a stall shower shown in Figures 7 and 8, below, is acceptable as-of-right in secondary bathrooms designed and constructed pursuant to item 2.1 of Section 1101.3.2 of the Building Code. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-001]</HIGHLIGHTER>
